title: Edeni Vegan
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Buffet, Mediterranean, Juice bar, Take-out, Hungarian
description: Eden Vegetarianus Etterem is a cafeteria style restaurant that offers a changing menu. Food is vegan. The only non-vegan items is honey in a few drinks and desserts. Has fresh juices. Hungarian, English, German and Serbo Croat spoken. At corner of Gyorskocsi utca, 1 block from Battány tér bus and metro station, 1 blk from the Danube.
